{"tid":974392,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"70","createTime":"2019-01-08T23:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T23:49:33.000Z","uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3250840dfe0695c8da4d11b10fe5e1e29e4d11ec","tid":974392,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T23:42:27.000Z","msg":"每次都係咁樣<br />\n<br />\n冇突發事<br />\n<br />\n冇人比壓力<br />\n<br />\n冇誘因冇導火線冇刺激<br />\n<br />\n但啲腦呀心呀手呀腳呀全部失去自控咁除左好辛苦以外<br />\n<br />\n乜都感受唔到<br />\n<br />\n按時食藥真係冇唔開心<br />\n<br />\n但有一舊無形既野徘徊體內<br />\n<br />\n不斷衝擊價值觀<br />\n<br />\n不斷想扯我落地獄咁<br />\n<br />\n一有呢舊野出現<br />\n<br />\n我就乜都控制唔住咁<br />\n<br />\n好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n好憎呢舊野<br />\n<br />\n只要佢冇左我就會搵事做？<br />\n<br />\n應該係<br />\n<br />\n有佢係度我乜都做唔到"},{"pid":"9a9645fe7b13d8d1c5c73422dd27ca77310aca03","tid":974392,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T23:45:08.000Z","msg":"祝福<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb62d80165e12a4f4cb15b5e0d043947ecaa3b3","tid":974392,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T23:49:33.000Z","msg":"打柒佢"}]}